score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T20:00:42.000Z","msg":"巴打有心，幫推"},{"pid":"6f3afee786fced29c4a5a749e4e933630c4455dc","tid":1317582,"uid":2110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T20:02:50.000Z","msg":"留名過兩日再推，今日有更重要既文宣"},{"pid":"beb1c714189488389f03af52eea490b994663d40","tid":1317582,"uid":269712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T20:04:07.000Z","msg":"旺角同今次都係俾狗包抄有咩方法避免 呢點好重要 因為係沙田法院就有37位手足因為包抄而被捕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"428196fd73aa12c6d934567a999b493f41468fdf","tid":1317582,"uid":11698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"70c69cfa93755180b2c3fa9feea6e8a81ad62bbc","tid":1317582,"uid":258373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T20:00:42.000Z","msg":"巴打有心，幫推"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T20:04:33.000Z","msg":"完全訓唔到，聽日仲有個interview，放飛機算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"198d349df5badb8e5e74c38761fd0b9a3fbb4fb3","tid":1317582,"uid":15625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T20:07:23.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"c604dcb77e2d4ead8a461c40410ca1e7883e5378","tid":1317582,"uid":11698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"beb1c714189488389f03af52eea490b994663d40","tid":1317582,"uid":269712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T20:04:07.000Z","msg":"旺角同今次都係俾狗包抄有咩方法避免 呢點好重要 因為係沙田法院就有37位手足因為包抄而被捕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T20:07:29.000Z","msg":"其實個邊個37位手足，我唔係太清楚點解佢地會去左個頭，十字路口多數都由沙田廣場退返去新城市中心，佢地係商場行出去定十字路口被迫去咗嗰度？"}]}